<div id="contactInfo" class="left">
	<h3>How To Contact:</h3>
	<p>The easiest way to get in touch with me is to fill out the form on the right, but here are a few other options if that just wonâ€™t work.</p>
	<h6>Phone:</h6>
	<p>{{{data.phone}}}</p>
	<h6>Email:</h6>
	<p><a href="mailto:{{{data.email}}}">{{{data.email}}}</a></p>
	<h6>Mailing Address:</h6>
	<p>Let's just say it is probably easier to use one of the other contact methods available, or just fill out the form on the right!</p>
</div>
<fieldset class="right">
	<h1>{{{data.heading}}}</h1>
	<p>{{{data.copy}}}</p>
	<form id="contactForm" action="/contact/sendmsg" method="post">
		<label class="hideText">Name</label><input type="text" name="fullname" class="field" id="name" value="Name"/>
		<label class="hideText">Email Address</label><input type="text" class="field" name="email" id="email" value="Email Address"/>
		<div id="subject">
			<span>Why Contact Derrick Showers?</span>
			<ul id="subjectOptions">
				<li id="learnmore">I Want a Website!</li>
				<li id="hire">I'm Interested In Learning More</li>
				<li id="career">I Have A Career Opportunity</li>
			</ul>
		<img src="/img/btn_arrowDown.gif" id="arrowDown" alt="Subject Select" />
		</div>
		<label class="hideText">Message</label><textarea class="field" id="message" name="message" maxlength="1205">Message</textarea>
		<button id="submit" class="btn-primary btn" name="submit" type="submit" value="yes">Submit</button>
		<input type="hidden" name="subject" value="none" />
	</form>
</fieldset>